Subject: Invoice Attached â€“ Immediate Review Required
Sender: billing@unknownvendor.net

Indicators Observed:

Unknown sender

Unexpected attachment

No prior business relationship

Generic greeting

Classification:

Suspicious

Risk Explanation:

Such emails often contain malware attachments. Opening the file may infect the system or allow unauthorized access.
